<main class="main">

  <section class="form-section" id="join" aria-label="Join the waitlist">
    <div class="form-section__inner">
      <div class="form-section__copy" data-reveal>
        <h2 class="form-section__heading">Know before<br>you sell.</h2>
        <p class="form-section__sub">Be first to know what your gear is actually worth. Founding members get early access before PowVal opens to the public.</p>
        <p class="form-section__proof">
          <span class="form-section__proof-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          Founding member list is open
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="form-card" data-reveal data-delay="80">
        <div id="waitlist-app"><noscript><p class="form-noscript">Please enable JavaScript to join the waitlist.</p></noscript></div>
      </div>
      <p class="form-section__founder" data-reveal data-delay="160">
        Built in Adelaide by Will, a skier who got tired of guessing what a season's setup was worth.
      </p>
      <p class="form-section__crosslink" data-reveal data-delay="200">
        <a href="#shops">Run a ski shop? Get trade-in pricing <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pillars" id="why" aria-label="What PowVal does">
    <div class="pillars__inner">
      <div class="pillar" data-reveal>
        <h3 class="pillar__head">Sold prices, not asking</h3>
        <p class="pillar__body">Every estimate is built from completed eBay sales: the prices buyers actually paid, refreshed every week.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar" data-reveal data-delay="80">
        <h3 class="pillar__head">Six factors priced in</h3>
        <p class="pillar__body">Year, length, condition, bindings, category, and region. The variables that actually move ski gear prices, weighted on real data.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar" data-reveal data-delay="160">
        <h3 class="pillar__head">Buy &amp; sell</h3>
        <p class="pillar__body">List directly to buyers who already know what your gear is. No explaining what a QST 92 is.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="shops" id="shops" aria-label="For ski shops">
    <div class="shops__inner">
      <div class="shops__copy" data-reveal>
        <span class="shops__tag">For ski shops</span>
        <h2 class="shops__heading">Price every trade-in with confidence.</h2>
        <p class="shops__sub">Value used and trade-in stock on the same real sold data, in bulk. Quote fair trade-ins on the spot, and catch overpriced inventory before it sits all season.</p>
        <ul class="shops__points">
          <li class="shops__point">
            <span class="shops__point-head">Bulk valuations</span>
            <span class="shops__point-body">Price a full rack of trade-ins at once, not one item at a time.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="shops__point">
            <span class="shops__point-head">Fair trade-in quotes</span>
            <span class="shops__point-body">Back every offer with what the gear actually sells for, so your margins hold.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="shops__point">
            <span class="shops__point-head">Less dead stock</span>
            <span class="shops__point-body">Spot overpriced inventory early and move it before the season ends.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="shops__card" data-reveal data-delay="80">
        <p class="shops__card-title">Get shop access early</p>
        <div id="shop-app"><noscript><p class="form-noscript">Please enable JavaScript to request shop access.</p></noscript></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>

